{"title":"发太空财","authors":["池北偶　朱根华"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":5,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"发太空财"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶  诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱根华  画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国的一些资本家热衷于从太空攫取巨额利润，竞相大做发行太空股票、销售月球地产等投机生意，诱骗人们入彀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人异想天开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄想大发横财。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地上不易赚钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算盘打到天外。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展开星球大战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纷纷摆设擂台。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或发太空股票，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"专向股民招徕；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或售月亮地皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诱骗炒家购买。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣传投资一块，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日后赚回几百。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信或不信由你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸿福岂会飞来？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地道投机生意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纯粹空头买卖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成交出于自愿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上当就是活该。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如此蹩脚把戏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只能糊弄蠢材。（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}